Text: Re smubetas FW party picsGreat Picshow do you remain so skinny when everyone else is getting so fat At AM you wrote Chuck Paul A Closer Look Professional Mystery Shopping Company Email Chuck CloserLookcom Original Message From Chuck Paul mailto Sent Monday August AM To SMUBetas Subject FW party pics Brother Betas Last night we had a GREAT Beta gathering here in Atlanta The pictures were taken at John Millers house In attendance Betas John Miller Randall Harman John Grumbles and Mark Hillstrom and myself We also had Rita Harman and their two kids Meredith and Kyle Woodys sons Matt and Adam as well as Mark Hillstroms son Ryan Marks son was in Atlanta to play in the US Amateur golf championship We feasted on Woodys great ribs and his Awesome Woody Blossom and drank a few too many beers you cant see us singing in a couple of the pictures but we did Foosball was one of the activities as was a phone call to Phil and Annie Morrow in Rockford Il The picture of John Miller is NOT with his wife April its with Randall Harmans daughter Meredith Some things never change thank God and Wooglin enjoy the pics kai Chuck PS Homecoming is the weekend of October thbe there Beta tailgating on campuswhat could be better Chuck Paul A Closer Look Professional Mystery Shopping Company Email Chuck CloserLookcom Original Message From Mario Muth mailto Sent Sunday August PM To Chuck Paul Subject party pics To unsubscribe from this group send an email to Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to infoterms Attachment Converted CPIPEPLUSDOWNLOADIMGjpg Attachment Converted CPIPEPLUSDOWNLOADIMGjpg Attachment Converted CPIPEPLUSDOWNLOADIMGjpg Attachment Converted CPIPEPLUSDOWNLOADIMGjpg Attachment Converted CPIPEPLUSDOWNLOADIMGjpg Attachment Converted CPIPEPLUSDOWNLOADIMGjpg Attachment Converted CPIPEPLUSDOWNLOADIMGjpg To unsubscribe from this group send an email to Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to infoterms
